.com/bestsellers/images/9781538773420.jpg" /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;海顿·潘妮蒂尔的《这就是我》&lt;br /&gt;这位金球奖提名女演员讲述了她如何与名誉抗衡并处理生活中的困难。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 May 2026 03:27:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.amazon.com/dp/1538773422?tag=thenewyorktim-20</guid></item><item><title>如何统治世界</title><link>https://www.amazon.com/dp/0593832833?tag=thenewyorktim-20</link><description>&lt;img src="https://static01.nyt.com/bestsellers/images/9780593832837.jpg" /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;《如何统治世界》作者：Theo Baker&lt;br /&gt;这位斯坦福大学的学生记录了他的调查，该调查帮助结束了马克·泰西尔·拉维涅 (Marc Tessier-Lavigne) 的校长任期。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 May 2026 03:27:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.amazon.com/dp/0593832833?tag=thenewyorktim-20</guid></item><item><title>所有美国爱国主义</title><link>https://www.amazon.com/dp/006351527X?tag=thenewyorktim-20</link><description>&lt;img src="https://static01.nyt.com/bestsellers/images/9780063515277.jpg" /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;所有美国爱国主义 雷切尔·坎波斯·达菲 (Rachel Campos-Duffy)&lt;br /&gt; “福克斯与朋友周末”的联合主持人汇集了歌曲、故事和照片来庆祝美国。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 May 2026 03:27:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.amazon.com/dp/006351527X?tag=thenewyorktim-20</guid></item><item><title>伊曼纽尔·诺贝尔失落的帝国</title><link>https://www.amazon.com/dp/1668074745?tag=thenewyorktim-20</link><description>&lt;img src="https://static01.nyt.com/bestsellers/images/9781668074749.jpg" /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;道格拉斯·布伦特《伊曼纽尔·诺贝尔失落的帝国》&lt;br /&gt; 《鲁道夫·迪塞尔神秘事件》一书的作者详细介绍了伊曼纽尔·诺贝尔被忽视的生活和工作。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 May 2026 03:27:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.amazon.com/dp/1668074745?tag=thenewyorktim-20</guid></item><item><title>一个不方便的寡妇</title><link>https://www.amazon.com/dp/1982140720?tag=thenewyorktim-20</link><description>&lt;img src="https://static01.nyt.com/bestsellers/images/9781982140724.jpg" /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;洛伊丝·罗马诺《不方便的寡妇》&lt;br /&gt;饱受诟病的前第一夫人玛丽·托德·林肯的传记。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 May 2026 03:27:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.amazon.com/dp/1982140720?tag=thenewyorktim-20</guid></item><item><title>参议员的教育</title><link>https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0FWZX15NQ?tag=thenewyorktim-20</link><description>&lt;img src="https://static01.nyt.com/bestsellers/images/9798895656488.jpg" /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;拉马尔·亚历山大的《参议员的教育》&lt;br /&gt;这位田纳西州前参议员兼教育部长详细介绍了他在美国政坛的六十年经历。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 May 2026 03:27:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0FWZX15NQ?tag=thenewyorktim-20</guid></item><item><title>自杀同理心</title><link>https://www.amazon.com/dp/0063446537?tag=thenewyorktim-20</link><description>&lt;img src="https://static01.nyt.com/bestsellers/images/9780063446533.jpg" /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;加德·萨德的《自杀同理心》&lt;br /&gt;播客“萨阿德真相”的主持人认为，他认为被误导的同情心正在对社会产生负面影响。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 May 2026 23:10:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.amazon.com/dp/0063446537?tag=thenewyorktim-20</guid></item></channel></rss>